Fresh EBT got a makeover! We’ve redesigned Fresh EBT to make it easier to manage your benefits, save money with discounts and offers, and earn income with new job & gig opportunities. In addition to this new look, you can still see your EBT balance instantly, find stores that accept EBT, make a list to help you stay in budget, and explore affordable recipes in the app.
